<h3>About this site</h3>
<h4>What is this site about?</h4>
<p>This site is for finding events right in your city.</p>
<p>This site about finding someone to accompany you for a event</p>
<p>This site is about getting more people to know about some event that you are organizing.</p>
<h4>Is this site for me?</h4>
<p>Yes it is, if you want to do something different than you normally do. Or if you cant involve friends in something that you are interested but is not fun to do alone. Do you have an extra movie/concert ticket? Are looking for a workout buddy? Are you organizing a event and want more people to participate? Are you planning a support march? </p>
<p>If anyone of the above or anything similar applies to you, then this site is definitely for you!!! </p>
<p>Enjoy the company!!!</p>

